{"lemma":"خَصْلَةٌ","slug":"خَصْلَةٌ","root":"خ.ص.ل","root_slug":"خ-ص-ل","root_link":"/words/roots/خ-ص-ل","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":7},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n10802"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AE%D9%8E%D8%B5%D9%92%D9%84%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"lock of hair, tress"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"tuft, wisp (of hair or wool)"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"disheveled hair"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"cluster or bunch of grapes"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"quality, feature, characteristic"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"a moral quality, a trait"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"a habit, a manner"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Instance noun from the root خ ص ل (ḵ ṣ l)."},"ipa":["/xusˤ.la/","/xasˤ.la/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n10802","headword_ar":"خَصْلَةٌ","root":"xSl","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xal~apN","text_ar":"خَلَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, K:) i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A property, quality, nature,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"disposition:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a habit,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"custom:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(KL, PS, TK:) [and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a practice,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an action:"},{"kind":"text","text":"it is used in these various senses in different trads.: in one trad., avarice is termed a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaSolap","text_ar":"خَصْلَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and so is evilness of nature: in another, fasting, and praying: in another, the inflicting of castigation, and the executing of retaliation, in a mosque:] it signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an excellent quality"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a low, base,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mean, quality"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA;) in a man: (TA:) or its predominant application is to"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an excellent quality"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) so in the M: (TA:) [it is said that] it is used only in commendation; whereas"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xal~apN","text_ar":"خَلَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is used in relation to good and evil: (Ham p. 525:) [but this is a mistake, as I have shown above:] accord. to Az, it signifies the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"states,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"conditions, of things"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"affairs:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) [or this is a signification of the pl.:] the pl. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xiSaAlN","text_ar":"خِصَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaSalaAtN","text_ar":"خَصَلَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;) [and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaSaAy^ilu","text_ar":"خَصَايِلُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"is a pl. pl., i. e. pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xiSaAlN","text_ar":"خِصَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", with which it is explained in the KL as syn.: see an ex. in a verse cited voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dafiy^N","text_ar":"دَفِيٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]       -A2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A hitting of the target;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K;) in shooting: (TA:) or, (K,) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaSolN","text_ar":"خَصْلٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (JK, K,) in a shooting-match, (JK,) it is ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a shot"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the case in which the arrow goes close by the target:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, K: *) thus accord. to Lth, who says that the former explanation is erroneous; (TA;) [as appears also from the assertion that] what are termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaSolataAni","text_ar":"خَصْلَتَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in a shooting-match, are reckoned as equivalent to a shot that goes right to the target. (T, K, TA.) ―         -b2-  And accord. to Sgh,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A single act of overcoming in a shooting-match."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)       -A3-  Also, and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuSolapN","text_ar":"خُصْلَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A raceme,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bunch,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of grapes or the like; syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EunoquwdN","text_ar":"عُنْقُودٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) ―         -b2-  And (both words)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A stick, branch,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"twig,"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EuwdN","text_ar":"عُودٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":",)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in which are thorns."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaSolapN","text_ar":"خَصْلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaSalapN","text_ar":"خَصَلَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", or this latter only, The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"extremity of a fresh, pliant, soft,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tender, twig,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rod:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, * TA:) and (some say, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a soft and tender twig"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rod, of the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"species of mimosa called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EurofuT","text_ar":"عُرْفُط"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K, TA:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaSolN","text_ar":"خَصْلٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[of which"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaSolapN","text_ar":"خَصْلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is the n. un.] signifies the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"slender extremities and branches of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EurofuT","text_ar":"عُرْفُط"},{"kind":"text","text":": (JK:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuSolapN","text_ar":"خُصْلَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a soft and tender branch of any tree:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, TA:) and [its pl.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuSalN","text_ar":"خُصَلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pendent extremities of trees."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","K","KL","PS","TK","TA","JK","T"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}